plot: Jo struggles with her new independence and the pull of her relationship with Slade. Jeana, Jo, Lauri and Vicki attend the Orange County Home & Garden Expo, where unresolved tension between Jo and Lauri caused by Lauri's relationship with Slade, comes to a head. Meanwhile, Tammy's rebellious daughter Megan takes her to a Pit Bull breed show. And Vicki has a hard time letting go of her obsession with work and her daughter, Briana.—Anonymous
